此应用使用电话权限读取手机信息并选择正确版本的frida，使用存储权限读取外部存储中的frida文件用于安装。如果您拒绝这些权限，程序将退出。

Frida server is not supported on this device.
Probable reasons
1. Android API Level not supported (Android R or higher is not supported now)
2. Device ABI not supported (only supports arm, arm64, x86, x86_64)
